RV Parking for an additional Monthly fee. The open floor plan has plenty of room for a dining and full family room set of furniture with two large windows and a bar. The two bedrooms each have a full size bathrooms. NEW VINYL PLANK FLOORING, AND PLUSH CARPET, Seller is offering buydown rates with his preferred lender from 10/31/2023- 11/30/2023, all the way down to 5.5%.
